   2  ''' 
   3  Peach 2 DOM.  Peach XML files are parsed into an object model using 
   4  these classes.  The document object is Peach and all objects extend 
   5  from Element. 
   6   
   7  Elements used inside of <DataModel>'s are called data elements and 
   8  extend from DataElement.  This also allows easy checking for a data 
   9  element vs. a relation or other object by saying 
  10  isinstance(obj, DataElement). 
  11   
  12  For speed, a native deepcopy was implemented in cDeepCopy, also 
  13  some of the tree walking code for locating objects by name is 
  14  done in native code for performance reasons (see cPeach). 
  15   
  16  API documentation is generated using epydoc and the script 
  17  tools\gendocs.bat.  Output ends up in docs\apidocs\index.html. 
  18
